@tysonnorris I have improved the logic to now explicitly pull `nightly` tagged images. 

So far the logic was explicitly checking via `docker images` command to check if image exist locally. This works fine for normal tagged images which in general do not get updated. However as nightly image do get updated this logic did not worked properly. Now for nightly even if the image is present locally it would be explicitly pulled.

Please try again with latest PR branch state

